    </list>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">宇宙</item>
        <item xml:lang="och">六合</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>PLACE AND TIME which CONTAINS ALL ABSTRACT AND CONCRETE THINGS.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The most current word for the whole universe is tiān dì 天地</p>
<p>2. Liù hé 六合 is a technical term referring to the world in all its dimensions from east to west, south to north, below to above.</p>
<p>3. Yǔ zhòu 宇宙 is a rather abstract cosmological word for the universe of space and time.</p>
        </div>
